title: La Traviata
typeOfFood: Lacto, Pizza, Italian, Organic, Beer/Wine, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Rooftop al fresco Italian dining with comfortable seating. Take elevator 4 flights, then walk up a set of stairs. Many salads and drinks. Flexible approach to menu items - let the staff know if vegan. Apr 2016 reported not stocking vegan cheese.
